<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sign-Up Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
  <table style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px;">
        <h2>Welcome to Our My Commerce!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for signing up. Your account has been successfully created.</p>
        <p>Please click the button below to confirm your email address:</p>
        <a href="<%= url %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #007BFF; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Confirm Email</a>
        <p>If you did not create this account, please disregard this email.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
